{"tid":103913,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 巴士上對話","createTime":"2017-02-01T16:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T02:32:02.000Z","uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d60f0c6c3dc47a58fa1f4df9dfafe697b7b128a","tid":103913,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T16:33:09.000Z","msg":"話說我上車坐下層尾二個行<br />\n一坐低 已經一直聽到後面2個女傾計<br />\n傾睇演唱會啲野 同朋友是非<br />\n一直我都冇點留意後面傾計<br />\n<br />\n突然 有一把男聲插入對話<br />\n不過完全同啲女講既野 唔啦間<br />\n個男既一直自己講賭波啲野<br />\n隊名 賠率買幾錢又剩<br />\n見2個女好尷尬又答佢唔到 係咁話係咩係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但個男又一直講落去<br />\n覺得個男仔真係好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔識開話題 真係慘過食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申屎都冇得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5e8efc9a7999a61d3707f9b630eaeac9abead0","tid":103913,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T16:35:24.000Z","msg":"個兩個女慘啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7499867a165d58a8b84a6839b45f4a9a2c0aab17","tid":103913,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T16:37:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個兩個女慘啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主慘啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a27d2f4fa54f011c6ce15a679ec8a5446767719","tid":103913,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T16:37:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個兩個女慘啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見有次 2個女答完男既<br />\n轉番自己話題   唔夠3句<br />\n又比個男既亂入<br />\n<br />\n真係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e492034e8d83b695254f8d0e261628a43b26